{"tid":1774832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大波驊真係俾人夾返嚟","createTime":"2019-12-08T13:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T13:32:06.000Z","uid":4574,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"26e77201f86f766c3df42000cb41e9d047f753f9","tid":1774832,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T13:16:20.000Z","msg":"《金融時報》引消息：鄭若驊盼辭職留英 終被北京下令回港<br />\n<br />\n律政司司長鄭若驊上月訪問英國倫敦時被示威者包圍時跌倒，她在英國接受手術後再到北京治療，至上周二（3日）才回港。<span style=\"color: red;\">英國《金融時報》引述三名知情人士稱，鄭若驊其實希望辭職並留在倫敦，但北京卻下令她要回港。</span><br />\n<br />\n報道指，律政司司長辦公室否認鄭若驊想辭職，亦否認北京曾經下令她回港。<br />\n<br />\n上月 14 日，鄭若驊出席特許仲裁學會舉辦的講座「Alexander Lecture 2019」並發表演說，她到場時被數十名示威者包圍，她在混亂中跌倒。她之後發稿嚴厲斥責「暴徒」令她身體受到嚴重傷害，已即時向倫敦警察報案，並要求當地警方嚴肅跟進將「兇徒」繩之於法。她又在中國駐倫敦大使館見記者，提到自己左手腕脫臼兼骨折，可能要一年才能正常活動。<br />\n<br />\n到上周二（3日）鄭若驊回港並在機場見記者，透露自己在英國接受手術後，再到北京作進一步治療，出院後已立即回港。被問到為何要到北京治療，而非回港就醫，她僅稱這是大使館安排。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%99%82%E5%A0%B1-%E5%BC%95%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E9%84%AD%E8%8B%A5%E9%A9%8A%E7%9B%BC%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7%E7%95%99%E8%8B%B1-%E7%B5%82%E8%A2%AB%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF/?fbclid=IwAR1WidL7rXYUPC9FC6ePspvH4XHqbhsbYMs5-RasDI4wydEnnIylqDu_N2M#.Xez12R-inbY.facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%258B%25A5%25E9%25A9%258A%25E7%259B%25BC%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E8%2581%25B7%25E7%2595%2599%25E8%258B%25B1-%25E7%25B5%2582%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E4%25B8%258B%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25B8%25AF%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1WidL7rXYUPC9FC6ePspvH4XHqbhsbYMs5-RasDI4wydEnnIylqDu_N2M%23.Xez12R-inbY.facebook&d=u6uLjzzFZj4TH%2F5rj7EkcxjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=fa481dac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%258B%25A5%25E9%25A9%258A%25E7%259B%25BC%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E8%2581%25B7%25E7%2595%2599%25E8%258B%25B1-%25E7%25B5%2582%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E4%25B8%258B%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25B8%25AF%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1WidL7rXYUPC9FC6ePspvH4XHqbhsbYMs5-RasDI4wydEnnIylqDu_N2M%23.Xez12R-inbY.facebook&h=5d1a8b4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%99%82%E5%A0%B1-%E5%BC%95%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E9%84%AD%E8%8B%A5%E9%A9%8A%E7%9B%BC%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7%E7%95%99%E8%8B%B1-%E7%B5%82%E8%A2%AB%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF/?fbclid=IwAR1WidL7rXYUPC9FC6ePspvH4XHqbhsbYMs5-RasDI4wydEnnIylqDu_N2M#.Xez12R-inbY.facebook</a>"},{"pid":"3b8089c555522a0b121fbdc83d259efc037422b1","tid":1774832,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T13:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e62031b685a9f9254e37d9c56df00a41aa4d788","tid":1774832,"uid":73340,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T13:20:30.000Z","msg":"咁大波連北京都忍不住要玩玩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3553241126ebc863d7cb4e65ff00e5174b142f","tid":1774832,"uid":9542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T13:23:07.000Z","msg":"其實佢驚咩，點解係香港遞信，驚無做會無popo 保，比示威者/中共融左？"},{"pid":"1270ec424be1bcf2c8e7a16ee267a7dcd951793a","tid":1774832,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T13:23:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實佢驚咩，點解唔係香港遞信，驚無做會無popo 保，比示威者/中共融左？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b9e55f775f17873fabb734c8ac691d3c279e4280","tid":1774832,"uid":212168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1270ec424be1bcf2c8e7a16ee267a7dcd951793a","tid":1774832,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T13:23:21.000Z"